{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the orphanage was run by Jewish-- Orthodox Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And now, we had been baptized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were raised in the convent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had gone to church every Sunday, at least four times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were very Catholic, especially my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In this orphanage, we, we went to school during the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They had classes for us in mathematics and Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And on Friday evenings, they would have a Sabbath celebration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And at-- and I liked it so much because it was festive, and the people, we sang songs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And of course, I loved to sing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we said prayers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And because of the festivities, it looked like there was more food too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My brother, George, had a hard time because he had to wear a yarmulke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He didn't want to wear a yarmulke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And that worried me because I thought he wouldn't get anything to eat, and then-- [LAUGHS] I would have to share my food with him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He also objected when I would recite the prayers, the Jewish prayers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But it was there in Westerbork that I became conscious of my Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it was not, not something that I consciously thought about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I just thought about, well, it was nice to pray.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was nice to sing, You know, to see-- to have some schooling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The people were nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "When we first came there, we got a slice of bread and butter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And it was much better for me, I thought, than Vught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "George was with the boys, but we came together at meal time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I knew we were in the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the, the orphanage barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a barrack that was for, for orphans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people in charge there, the people who were in charge.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
